      Chicago Medical School<br>
      Rosalind Franklin University of Medicine and Science</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-contact">
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p>
        Innovation and Research Park, Room 232<br>
        <a href="mailto:hongkyun.kim@rosalindfranklin.edu">hongkyun.kim@rosalindfranklin.edu</a><br>
